window.bookSummaryJSON = "Following <i>Blood and Iron</i> and <i>The Center Cannot Hold</i>, <i>The Victorious Opposition</i> triumphantly concludes Harry Turtledove's <i>American Empire</i> trilogy - a masterful saga of alternate history. War is brewing yet again as the U.S.A. struggles to occupy Canada, and the C.S.A. begins forcing blacks into concentration camps."; 
